                        <h1>KUMAR SANGAKKARA</h1>
                        <h2 class="subheading">Adieu To The </h2>
                        <span class="meta">Posted by <a href="#">Daily Dose</a> on August 23, 2015</span>
                    </div>
<h2 class="subheading"><font-color="white">Written By- Himansu Jha</font></h2>
